			</BitmapImage>
		</Group>
		<RichText x="738" y="223" width="424" height="85" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">处在较远的地方时，遗迹重机侧身朝玩家处快速移动，期间碰到造成<span color="#b9b9b9">30%</span><span>伤害，冲刺开始与结束时造成</span><span color="#b9b9b9">40%</span><span>伤害。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="738" y="447" width="424" height="85" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">遗迹重机上半身快速旋转，并朝玩家走来，扫击范围内持续造成<span color="#b8b8b8">60%</span><span>伤害，双腿核心大概率暴露。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="738" y="671" width="424" height="143" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">遗迹重机短暂暴露头部核心，发射一枚大型混沌球，其分裂成3个小型混沌球，并呈三角状分布在玩家周围，触碰持续造成<span color="#b8b8b8">16%</span><span>伤害。</span><span color="#bfffbf">(特异体)</span><span>大型混沌球连续分裂3次后消失。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="738" y="927" width="424" height="85" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">遗迹重机迈出右脚踩下，造成<span color="#b8b8b8">40%</span><span>伤害，随后暴露双腿核心，并产生一个更大范围的震波，造成</span><span color="#b8b8b8">70%</span><span>伤害。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="738" y="1151" width="421" height="114" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#bfffbf">(特异体)<span color="#ffffff">遗迹重机进行右拳、左拳、转身、砸击共4段的普通攻击，依次造成</span><span color="#b9b9b9">30%,30%,30%,50%</span><span color="#ffffff">伤害，停留一下，使用激光对前方轰击，造成</span><span color="#b9b9b9">20%</span><span color="#ffffff">伤害。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="738" y="1375" width="423" height="143" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#bfffbf">(特异体)<span color="#ffffff">遗迹重机双手拼合，往地上插入形成推土机，造成</span><span color="#b9b9b9">40%</span><span color="#ffffff">伤害，期间不断冲向玩家，触碰造成</span><span color="#b9b9b9">30%</span><span color="#ffffff">伤害，接着拔起造成</span><span color="#b9b9b9">40%</span><span color="#ffffff">伤害，插入和拔起均短暂暴露双腿核心。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="738" y="1631" width="436" height="85" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#bfffbf">(特异体)<span color="#ffffff">遗迹重机生命值为0时，其缓慢恢复生命值至满，</span><span color="#ffbfbf">每秒恢复12.5%生命值</span><span color="#ffffff">，期间无法被任何攻击伤及。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<BitmapImage source="@Embed('/遗迹重机.assets/Image_14.png')" x="720" y="137">
		</BitmapImage>
