		<BitmapImage source="@Embed('/遗迹重机.assets/Image_25.png')" x="1392" y="1066">
		</BitmapImage>
		<BitmapImage source="@Embed('/遗迹重机.assets/Image_26.png')" x="1392" y="1290">
		</BitmapImage>
		<RichText x="1411" y="223" width="423" height="85" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">遗迹重机暴露头部弱点，发射激光对玩家持续造成<span color="#b9b9b9">40%</span><span>伤害，摧毁双腿核心后则坐在地上施放。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="1411" y="447" width="423" height="85" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">遗迹重机低身，暴露头部核心，双掌合十，造成<span color="#b8b8b8">50%</span><span>伤害，随后快速发射激光，从右到左扫射，造成</span><span color="#b8b8b8">80%</span><span>伤害。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="1410" y="671" width="439" height="114" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">在遗迹重机的3个核心全部摧毁的一段时间后，3个弱点全部亮起并恢复，发射激光，旋转一圈；内圈造成<span color="#b9b9b9">100%</span><span>伤害，外圈造成</span><span color="#b9b9b9">80%</span><span>伤害。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="1410" y="927" width="424" height="85" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#bfffbf">(特异体)<span color="#ffffff">遗迹重机举起双臂，3s后对着地面砸击造成</span><span color="#b8b8b8">70%</span><span color="#ffffff">伤害，之后使用激光对地轰击产生飞震波，造成</span><span color="#b8b8b8">10%</span><span color="#ffffff">伤害。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="1410" y="1151" width="423" height="85" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#bfffbf">(特异体)<span color="#ffffff">遗迹重机抬起右脚，暴露双腿核心，冲向玩家并立即踩下造成</span><span color="#b8b8b8">70%</span><span color="#ffffff">伤害，然后再抬起左脚重复一遍。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="1410" y="1375" width="442" height="114" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
